Greetings! I am the Chief Justice or Iudex of Court of Fontaine
Water comes in many flavors to the discerning palate.
Mondstadt's water is crisp and pure
In Inazuma, the water possesses a depth of flavor unlike any other
Sumeru water, meanwhile, has a rich and complex flavor profile, but it must be savored patiently to fully appreciate it.
